Read PNG figures into Binary Files

rtf_read_png.Rd

Read PNG figures into Binary Files

rtf_read_png(file)

Arguments

file

a vector of PNG file path

Value

a list of binary data vector returned by readBin

Examples

  file <- file.path(tempdir(), "figure1.png")
  png(file)
  plot(1:10)
  dev.off()
#> pdf 
#>   2 

  # Read in PNG file in binary format
  rtf_read_png(file)
